Package: com.zeshan.phoneaura
Name: PhoneAura
Version: 0.4.7
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64e
Description: Test-only Concept D update for RootHide. Adds All, Dialed, Received and Missed call filters, an in-app call-detail card from the info button, swipe-to-delete call records, swipe-to-delete contacts, a confirmed Delete Contact action inside contact details, and reduced repeated contact/history loading. Not for live-repo publication until device testing is approved.
Maintainer: Next Solution
Author: Next Solution
Section: Tweaks
Depends: firmware (>= 16.0), mobilesubstrate, preferenceloader
